Riding the F77s from Versailles to Dampierre with @narayan_uv, @varunsood12 and @harmansingha was super exciting.

Taking Ultraviolette from India, to the World.

#ultraviolette #F77 #makeinindia #europelaunch #ultraviolette_france

The Big Biker’s Draw has officially come to a close and what an incredible ride it’s been. Riders from all over came through, shared their love for the open road and brought the spirit of the journey alive at our stores.

Huge thanks to every single one of you who showed up and made this draw a massive success. The energy you brought was unbeatable.

Now, the moment you’ve been waiting for - the winners of the Big Biker’s Draw are in!

We’ve got two riders bagging action cameras, two more walking away with smartwatches and one lucky legend who won a Royal Enfield Himalayan 450.

Check the reel and hit up your nearest ReiseMoto store to claim what’s yours. To everyone else - stay ready. The road always has more in store.

*Winner from Chennai was chosen via The Big Bikers Giveaway based on the best slogan for what “Joy Of Riding” means to them. 

#BigBikersDraw #ReiseMoto #JoyOfRiding #Rannvijay #WinnersAnnounced #RoyalEnfield #RideWithReise
